{"tid":1445432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布不受傷不流血不被捕只係一句廢話 不服來辯","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:22:00.000Z","uid":200062,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f7434a0929f782fe730e18ceb6421805ab48e5c2","tid":1445432,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"見到傷亡慘重好心痛好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不受傷 不流血 不被捕 講左咁耐，但係成日得個講字，冇實踐到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗辦法係抗爭運動裡面真正實踐出黎好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要向暴政強權屈服，仍然要繼續上街，不過我地真係有必要避免不必要嘅犧牲，保護自己、保護手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐齊上齊落、一個都不能少，唔好得個講字，要真係實踐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後附上梁天琦信嘅一段：<br />\n當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我愛大家 加油 一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},